#: src/iacfleet.cpp:445
msgid "The dataset is available from Saildocs\n"
"Send an e-mail with the text\n"
"fleet.nadi\n"
"and any subject to query@saildocs.com\n"
"When you receive the response, copy and paste it to the Raw tab or save as text and open on the Files tab."
msgstr "El conjunto de datos está disponible en Saildocs\n"
